These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, biathlon, surfing
House: cape-cod, colonial, tower, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, hiking, woodworking, chess
1. the colonial house is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the tower house is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the colonial house is the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Sport   | skateboarding    | surfing    | water-polo      | biathlon    |
| House   | futuristic | colonial | tower | cape-cod |
| Hobby     | chess  | camping       | hiking    | woodworking     |

