.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, swisher, chaman, montecristo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
City: new-york, rome, colone, berlin
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, jazz, dubstep, blues
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is the fan of jazz##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person traveling to colone and the fan of classical##2
6. the fan of blues is between the person watching western movies and the person traveling to berlin##2
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | montecristo | swisher    | chaman  | bongani    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| City           | berlin      | colone       | rome      | new-york       |
| Music-Genre         | jazz    | blues | dubstep | classical |

