.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, chestnut, lavender, white
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, soccer, golf
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, blend, dunhill, bluemaster
1. the person who's sport is soccer is the blend-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who likes white##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes white##2
9. the person who likes lavender is between the person eating lemon and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Color       | chestnut   | brown   | lavender | white |
| Sport         | snowboarding   | soccer | golf       | cricket    |
| Cigar   | dunhill    | blend | prince  | bluemaster    |

