The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
House: futuristic, tower, cape-cod, victorian
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, filmmaking, drawing
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person playing whist##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the tower house##1
 6. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the person playing poker is between the futuristic house and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Game           | whist  | scrabble | poker     | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| House           | tower       | victorian    | cape-cod      | futuristic           |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | video-games   | drawing   | filmmaking         |

