There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, indian, french
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the canadian is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is the swisher-smoker##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the french and the siglo-smoker##2
10. the bluemaster-smoker is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Hobby           | card-games | singing | chess    | board-games     |
| Cigar   | siglo      | bluemaster       | blend    | swisher       |
| Nationality         | canadian     | indian       | french | german |

