.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, november, april
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There 4 different types of food: pear, artichoke, papaya, potato
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, goldfish, ferret
1. the fan of folk is between the owner of the ferret and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the fan of folk and the person eating potato##2
3. the person eating papaya is between the owner of the rabbit and the person eating artichoke##2
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
5. the person eating papaya is the person eating papaya##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday           | november | august | may  | april |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Food   | potato   | artichoke      | papaya   | pear   |
| Pet         | goldfish   | ferret    | hedgehog | rabbit   |

