 7. the townhouse house is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the gothic-revival house is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
