.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, 7up
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, trike, scooter, bus
City: berlin, paris, edinburgh, miami
 1. the person eating lettuce is the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person drinking juice is the person traveling to paris##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person driving the bus is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person traveling to berlin##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Beverage           | 7up | almond-milk | iced-tea   | juice |
| Transport   | scooter         | bike       | bus      | trike     |
| City         | edinburgh       | miami | berlin    | paris  |

